         <abstract id="aspace_0e2361ed81852c6673cd92d88c389f67">Correspondence, printed matter, photographs and memorabilia reflecting the friendship of Mary Geran with members of the Greek royal family and with members of the German nobility. The largest number of letters are from Lilo Scholz, Marguerite, Landgräfin of Hesse, Grand Duchess Helen of Russia and from Sophia, princess of Greece.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Starr, Mary M. Geran</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
